h soda or juice. What does the cocktail look like? What does it taste like? Who prepared it?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They ordered cocktail... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) cocktail party<br />\n\t2) cocktail menu<br />\n\t3) ordering a cocktail<br />\n\t4) coming up with a cocktail recipe<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHodge had to spend money on decorations, advertising, and updating the menu, especially coming up with specialty cocktails. These drinks were big money-makers. Since the alcohol content of a cocktail was lower than a regular alcoholic drink like beer or wine, customers were able to consume more cocktails. On top of that, a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/premium\" target=\"_blank\">premium</a> could be charged for the specialty items as they looked a lot fancier. When these drink were introduced, they usually came as a set with the same theme. With a colorful design and eye-catching decorations, customers would have fun tasting these cocktails.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167973582090/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799321/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799321\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p800240/\">里约奥运会各国队服大PK：哪家爆潮哪家逗比</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p786128/\">励志美文：毕业后，如何正视自己？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p803342/\">澳大利亚代表队 大概是里约奥运最大的倒霉蛋</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2